### create chat
POST http://localhost:6688/api/chats
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "acme",
    "members": [1, 2],
    "public": false
}

### get chat list
GET http://localhost:6688/api/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### get user list
GET http://localhost:6688/api/users
